opencode-cc-camouflage is a companion maintenance plugin scaffold.

This repository includes source snapshots in `fixtures/` for development and
patch verification:
- `opencode-anthropic-auth` (MIT, https://github.com/ex-machina-co/opencode-anthropic-auth)
- `not-claude-code-emulator` as a reference fixture (README only; upstream has
  no LICENSE file and its `package.json` declares MIT)

These fixtures are kept in git for local work, but they are excluded from the
npm published package via the `package.json` `files` field.
